Creating new users in MYsql:

1. https://www.a2hosting.in/kb/developer-corner/mysql/managing-mysql-databases-and-users-from-the-command-line
2. https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-create-a-new-user-and-grant-permissions-in-mysql
3. https://dev.mysql.com/doc/refman/8.0/en/adding-users.html


CREATE USER 'finley'@'%' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';

GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'finley'@'%' WITH GRANT OPTION;

username: drupal
password: drupa@l123

CREATE USER 'drupal'@'%' IDENTIFIED BY 'drupal@123';
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'drupal'@'%' WITH GRANT OPTION;

Commnad for Connection:
mysql -h 52.55.62.38 -u drupal -pdrupal@123

Possible Error: ERROR 2003 (HY000): Can’t connect to MySQL server on ‘127.0.0.1’ (111)
Solution: https://www.tecmint.com/fix-error-2003-hy000-cant-connect-to-mysql-server-on-127-0-0-1-111/

